# Real-Time Contact Center Intelligence Platform

## Project Overview

This project is a real-time contact center analytics platform designed to simulate modern enterprise customer support monitoring systems used in large-scale cloud-native environments such as Amazon Connect operational analytics platforms.

The system streams live customer interaction events through Apache Kafka, processes them using distributed streaming architecture concepts, stores operational analytics data inside PostgreSQL, and visualizes business KPIs using an interactive Streamlit dashboard.

The platform demonstrates:

- Real-time event streaming
- Distributed analytics pipeline architecture
- Operational intelligence monitoring
- SLA breach analytics
- Customer sentiment analysis
- AI-powered anomaly detection
- Dashboard visualization
- Event-driven system design
- Data engineering concepts

This project resembles simplified versions of enterprise operational intelligence systems used in cloud contact centers and customer support analytics environments.

---

# Architecture

```text
Call Data Generator
      ↓
Kafka Producer
      ↓
Kafka Topic (call_records_topic)
      ↓
Streaming Consumer
      ↓
PostgreSQL Analytics Warehouse
      ↓
Streamlit Dashboard
```

---

# High-Level Architecture

```text
                ┌────────────────────────────┐
                │ Call Data Generator        │
                │ Customer Interaction Data  │
                └─────────────┬──────────────┘
                              │
                              ▼
                ┌────────────────────────────┐
                │ Kafka Producer             │
                │ Real-Time Streaming        │
                └─────────────┬──────────────┘
                              │
                              ▼
                ┌────────────────────────────┐
                │ Kafka Topic                │
                │ call_records_topic         │
                └─────────────┬──────────────┘
                              │
                              ▼
                ┌────────────────────────────┐
                │ Analytics Consumer         │
                │ Event Processing ETL       │
                └─────────────┬──────────────┘
                              │
                              ▼
                ┌────────────────────────────┐
                │ PostgreSQL Warehouse       │
                │ Analytics Storage          │
                └─────────────┬──────────────┘
                              │
                              ▼
                ┌────────────────────────────┐
                │ Streamlit Dashboard        │
                │ Live Operational Insights  │
                └────────────────────────────┘
```

